Steps to start

1. Pull the following images from https://hub.docker.com/
selenium/hub
selenium/node-firefox-debug
selenium/node-chrome-debug

2. Instructions for selenium/hub are in -> https://github.com/SeleniumHQ/docker-selenium/tree/master/Hub
To create the node run:
docker run -d -p 4646:4444 --name selenium-hub selenium/hub

3. Instructions for node-firefox-debug are in -> https://github.com/SeleniumHQ/docker-selenium/tree/master/NodeFirefoxDebug
To create the node run:
docker run -d -p 5902:5900 --link selenium-hub:hub -v /dev/shm:/dev/shm selenium/node-firefox-debug

4. Instructions for node-chrome-debug are in -> https://github.com/SeleniumHQ/docker-selenium/tree/master/NodeChromeDebug
To create the node run:
docker run -d -p 5903:5900 --link selenium-hub:hub -v /dev/shm:/dev/shm selenium/node-chrome-debug

5. 